name: Jabba's Palace Sabacc
Lore: 'Jabba has won the service of many of his guards and other henchbeings through games of chance.',
Text: 'Requirements: Gambler, gangster, smuggler or information broker at a Jabba''s Palace site.Wild cards (1-6): Passenger Deck and deserts.Clone cards: Aliens and Jabba''s Palace sites (gamblers and Jabba may use clones as 4).Stakes: One character weapon or non-unique alien.',
